Popular skit maker, Chukwuemeka Emmanuel Ejekwu, aka Oga Sabinus has landed a huge ambassadorial deal with Dangote. Sabinus took to the microblogging app to share the great news with his teeming fans.   My battle with sickle cell, by Adekunle Gold     Asake for maiden SPOB jive     Baba Ijesha: Yomi Fabiyi’s estranged lover cancels…   In his brief post, ‘investor” expressed heartfelt gratitude for the privilege to represent the number one brand in West Africa and the entire continent. Sharing photos from his recent outing at an event organised by the Dangote group, hosted by Frank Edoho, the comic act wrote: “Thanks Dangote cement for the opportunity to represent. #brandambassador.”